=== Known Issues & Solutions ===

## OpenRouter model_preference format
- DB column `user_api_keys.model_preference` for OpenRouter must store the full model ID (e.g. `openai/gpt-4o-mini`), NOT just the model name.
- Setting it to `gpt-4o-mini` causes the code to build `openrouter/gpt-4o-mini` which is invalid.
- Setting it to `openrouter/openrouter/auto` (with duplicate provider prefix) is also invalid.
- Valid: `openai/gpt-4o-mini`, `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-20250514`, etc.
